snippet.title: WaveCrash!! 2nd Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's our second trailer for the multiplayer puzzle brawler WaveCrash!! made in preparation for our upcoming demo at GDEX!

You can download WaveCrash!! at flyover-games.itch.io/wavecrash
